@node Preface

Section I. - Preface
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


   djpegGUI is an Intuition front end to the Independent JPEG Group's
   JPEG decompression software. ("djpeg")


   djpegGUI will run under Kickstart 2.04 and above only.


@endnode

